snippet.title: Zui's Witch Academy - Dance around rotating arenas in this roguelike bossrush!
snippet.description:
Made in about a month for the Boss Rush Game Jam! The theme for the game jam was spin! The bosses will rotate their arena in creative ways, synced up to the music and each one boasting an interesting gimmick!

Musician and sfx: Lunziestella
Main artist: Lunziestella
Coding: ScolonDev
Backup artist: ScolonDev
----------------------------------------
Play the game here!
https://lunziestella.itch.io/zuis-witch-academy
